Package ys.succinct.util

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BalancedParentheses
    An object that represents a set of the balanced parentheses and supports a number of the search operations on them.
    BitSet
    An object that represents a set of bits and allows read/write operations on them.
    BitVector
    An object that represents a set of bits and defines the rank/select operations on them.
    Rank
    An object that supports rank-based operations on the bit set that it wraps.
    Select
    An object that supports the select operation on the bit set that it wraps.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractRank
    An abstract implementation of Rank that expresses some operations via the underlying rank operation.
    CompactIntArray
    Compact representation of an array of the non-negative integers that requires smaller fixed number of bits per an element.
    IntBitSet
    A mutable bit set that either can have the fixed size or can grow as needed.
    IntRank
    A plain bit set that is able to answer Rank queries.
    ParenthesesUtils
    Utilities for handling the balanced parentheses.
    RangeTreeParentheses
    BalancedParentheses implementation based on the range min-max tree (see K.
    SamplingBitVector
    A plain bit vector that provides the rank/select operations.
